      "x": 100,
      "y": 460,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 60,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Executor 1 sends Election to higher IDs (102, 103)\n2. Executor 2 (103) doesn't respond (crashed)\n3. Executor 3 (102) responds OK and starts its own election\n4. Executor 3 sends Election to ID 103 (no response)",
